VIRAT KOHLI
Indian cricketer
DESCRIPTION
Description
Virat Kohli is an Indian cricketer and the current captain of the India national team. A right-handed top-order batsman, Kohli is regarded as one of the best contemporary batsmen in the world. Wikipedia
Born: 5 November 1988 (age 32 years), New Delhi
Height: 1.75 m
Weight: 69 kg
Spouse: Anushka Sharma (m. 2017)
Children: Vamika Kohli
Awards: Wisden Cricketers of the Year, Padma Shri, MORE
